snippet.title: Moe Shop - GHOST FOOD (feat. TORIENA)
snippet.description:
Stream/Download: https://moeshop.fanlink.to/ghostfood

Produced by Moe Shop
Lyrics & Vocals by TORIENA
Art by なるめ/narume
Design by GraphersRock

Lyrics (Japanese):

六畳一間僕のお城
だれも入れない秘密の場所Yeah
合言葉は一度きりの人生
部屋に入るときはノックしてね
じゃないとバットエンド
GhostのFood

リアルで絶対会うことないから
ネットの方が楽
でも他人の話に興味ねえから
笑って頷いてる
嘘考えるのがめんどくさいから
だいたい正直です
お菓子の空箱　嘘の香水
本名なんて何だっけ？

かわいいあの子は大体加工で
背景歪んでる
無機物絶対裏切らないから
視聴履歴アニメだらけ
太りたくないけど運動怠いし
ごはんの代わりがアイス
真夜中夜明け　高いラムネ
紫色のうさぎが歌う

六畳一間僕のお城
だれも入れない秘密の場所Yeah
言葉にしたらチープだから
心の中で唱える呪文

F-O-O-D

甘い言葉足らぬ頭
きっと生まれた時からある結末
グレーであるほう
無口である方
言葉疎い方が得策
言い訳ばっかりうまくなっていく
何にもない時間だけが過ぎる
本当は自分自身で気づいてるふりして
全然気づいてない

片道切符乗り込む環状線
腐食さんざめく心境
グレーであるほう
無口である方
言葉疎い方が得策
言い訳ばっかりうまくなって
だんだん毒が楔になって
本当は自分自身で気づいてるふりして
全然気づいてない

Lyrics (English):

This six-tatami room, here's my castle
A secret place nobody can enter -- Yeah
Here our motto is "You only live once"
Just knock before entering
Or else it's going to be a bad ending
Ghost Food

We'll never meet in real life
Online is where I relax
I've got no interest in what they've got to say
I just nod and smile
I can't be bothered making up a lie
I'm mostly honest
A littered box of sweets with the scent of deceit 
Just what was my name again?

That cute girl is manufactured
The background is distorted
These inorganic substances would never betray
My viewing history is full of anime
Don't want to put on weight, don't want to move a muscle
I'll have ice cream instead of food
From dusk to dawn, expensive soda
Or so the purple bunny sings

This six-tatami room, here's my castle
A secret place nobody can enter -- Yeah
Say it out loud and it sounds cheap
It's a spell to be chanted inside

F-O-O-D

There's not enough sweet words in my head
I'm sure this is how I was destined to be
When you're gray
When you're quiet
The less you speak the better
Just get better at making excuses
Time flying by all around you
Just pretending like it's something you notice
When you really don't

This one-way ticket to the ring road
This corroded state of mind
When you're gray
When you're quiet
The less you speak the better
Just get better at making excuses
The rot will just wedge deeper
Just pretending like it's something you notice
When you really don't

#MoeShop #TORIENA #GHOSTFOOD
